---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Balatro from '../components/Balatro.jsx';
---

<Layout title="About - Project Overlord" description="Learn more about Project Overlord">
  <div class="flex flex-col">
    <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center mb-12">
      <!-- Balatro Background -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-zinc-950">
        <Balatro isRotate={false} mouseInteraction={true} pixelFilter={700} client:load />
      </div>

      <!-- Overlay for better text readability -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 -bottom-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-950/30 via-zinc-950/50 to-zinc-950"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Hero Content -->
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center space-y-6 px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-50">
          About Project Overlord
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A minimalistic article site where I criticize many things
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full px-4 md:px-8 pb-12">
      <article class="prose prose-zinc prose-invert max-w-none">
        <h2>What Project Overlord <i>Is</i></h2>
        <p>
          Well it's not a safe space, not a place for sugarcoating, not a mainstream opinion farm,
          not here to please everyone. And definitely isn't a Libertarianist blog. /s
        </p>

        <h2>So what do you identify as?</h2>
        <p>
          Anyone who knows me, knows that I'm a Muslim with Libertarian values. On the political
          spectrum I identify myself as part of the right-wing libertarian movement even though it's
          not completely accurate. (Not all right-wing movements are the same btw, stop with that
          shit.)
        </p>

        <h2>Why the name "Project Overlord"?</h2>
        <p>Battle of Normandy. That's literally the only reason.</p>

        <hr class="w-full border-t border-white/20" />

        <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Astro</strong> - Fast, content-focused framework
          </li>
          <li><strong>React</strong> - Interactive components</li>
          <li><strong>Tailwind CSS v4</strong> - Modern styling</li>
          <li>
            <strong>Supabase</strong> - PostgreSQL database and APIs
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
